column5: Doe's anyone know if the Walmart in Dryden sells groceries now? Has it been converted into a Super Walmart?
The Wal-Mart only sells basic food items and is not a full grocery store but there is a nice grocery store across the street from the Wal-Mart.

Shoe is correct on the Walmart, limited food items. You might want to try the Safeway, they have good prices. The Safeway is located 2 blocks south of route 17 at the stop light by the Weyerhaeuser wood mill.
